<Link id="l01202" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1202"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// here.  Branch into if looks like this:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01203" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1203"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//                        entry</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01210" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1210"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01211" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1211"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// The diamond&#95;head block begins the &quot;if&quot; and the diamond&#95;true block</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01212" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1212"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// is the block being &quot;branched into&quot;.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01213" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1213"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01214" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1214"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// If MigrateTrue is true, then TrueBB is the block being &quot;branched into&quot;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01215" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1215"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// and if MigrateFalse is true, then FalseBB is the block being</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01216" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1216"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// &quot;branched into&quot;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01217" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1217"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01218" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1218"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Here is the pseudo code for how I think the optimization should work:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01219" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1219"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// 1 Insert MOV GPR0, 0 before the branch instruction in diamond&#95;head.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01220" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1220"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// 2 Insert MOV GPR0, 1 before the branch instruction in branch&#95;from.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01221" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1221"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// 3 Move the branch instruction from diamond&#95;head into its own basic</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01222" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1222"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//    block (new&#95;block).</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01223" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1223"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// 4 Add an unconditional branch from diamond&#95;head to new&#95;block</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01224" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1224"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// 5 Replace the branch instruction in branch&#95;from with an unconditional</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01225" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1225"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//    branch to new&#95;block.  If branch&#95;from has multiple predecessors, then</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01226" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1226"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//    we need to replace the True/False block in the branch</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01227" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1227"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//    instruction instead of replacing it.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01228" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1228"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// 6 Change the condition of the branch instruction in new&#95;block from</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01229" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1229"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//    COND to (COND || GPR0)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01230" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1230"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01231" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1231"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// In order insert these MOV instruction, we will need to use the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01232" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1232"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// RegisterScavenger.  Usually liveness stops being tracked during</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01233" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1233"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// the late machine optimization passes, however if we implement</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01234" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1234"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// bool TargetRegisterInfo::requiresRegisterScavenging(</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01235" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1235"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//                                                const MachineFunction &amp;MF)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01236" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1236"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// and have it return true, liveness will be tracked correctly</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01237" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1237"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// by generic optimization passes.  We will also need to make sure that</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01238" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1238"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// all of our target-specific passes that run after regalloc and before</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01239" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1239"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// the CFGStructurizer track liveness and we will need to modify this pass</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01240" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1240"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// to correctly track liveness.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01241" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1241"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01242" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1242"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// After the above changes, the new CFG should look like this:</span></CodeLine>
